Employee Term:

Microsoft:
Signout of Microsoft sessions 
Block Sign-in
  If needed:
    Add manager to Read and manage permissions 
    Go into OneDrive from make an access link > Put all contents into a folder > share folder with manager.
Remove all but E3 or E1 licenses to keep mailbox active while manager uses if needed. 

AD:
Remove any DL from account or app security groups 
Change password to random key if account must stay active
  When access is not needed, move user to Disabled or Term. OU

Okta: 
Search user > more actions > Deactivate


Keep term ticket open until no other users have access to the employess data and the laptop has been returned.

Show screen shots of needed steps in Term ticket. 
